    <p>Hey Tyty, I just want to say how incredibly grateful I am to know you. <i class="fas fa-heart" style="color: var(--primary);"></i></p>
    
    <p>From your beautiful smile to your adorable little typos, you're absolutely unforgettable. Whether you say <span class="quote">"thang"</span> instead of "thing" or <span class="quote">"godonight"</span> instead of "goodnight," I cherish every single part of you.</p>
    
    <p>You once said <span class="quote">"thxl"</span> and now it lives rent-free in my head <i class="fas fa-brain" style="color: var(--accent);"></i>. And let's not forget <span class="quote">"luv u"</span> and <span class="quote">"morninb"</span> — pure gold <i class="far fa-gem" style="color: #ffd700;"></i>.</p>
    
    <p>Your birthday, <strong class="date-highlight">July 22</strong>, is more than just a date. It's a celebration of the amazing person you are and a reminder of how lucky the world is to have you in it <i class="fas fa-globe-americas" style="color: #7cfc00;"></i></p>
    
