    <p>You're not just someone I know — you're someone I deeply admire, care about, and will always hold close to my heart.</p>
    
    <p>Here's to your special day, to your beautiful smile, your infectious laugh, and all the wonderful memories we've shared and those yet to come. <i class="fas fa-glass-cheers" style="color: var(--accent);"></i></p>
    
    <p>Happy Birthday again, my amazing Tyty. You mean the absolute world to me. <i class="fas fa-infinity" style="color: var(--primary);"></i></p>
    
